[recto] 57-58. Witt Library. Under L. van Valckenborch. A poorer photograph of the so-called C. Massys Good Shepherd [...] Erhardt Sale, Christie, 19-22 June, 1931; Andreas Mantuna 72. The Good Shepherd, signed, on panel -21 in.0 by 32 1/2in.; Signed in left hand corner "Andreas Mantuna" C.P.P. Bought by T. Harris. T. Harris says: By L. Valckenborch and signature 'Andreas Mantuna' is 19th Cent. forgery; [verso] Witt Library. L. van Valckenborch [Dr. Viktor] Bloch Sale, Gilhofer & Ranschburg Lucerne 30 Nov. 1934; L. Van Valckenborch 33. Die Parabel von ungetreue Hirte, mongrammiert LVV [schema] clearly based on Bruegel.
